Package: manifestos
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Modelling of Party Manifestos
Version: 0.7-1
Date: 2013-02-05  
Author: Martin Elff
Maintainer: Martin Elff <martin.elff@uni-konstanz.de>
Description: This package provides an MCEM algorithm to
  estimate the parameters of a spatial model for the
  reconstruction of policy positions of political actors,
  such as parties, based on manifesto data or, more generally,
  based on multinomial counts.
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: Yes
Depends: Matrix, mvtnorm, munfold, memisc, Rcpp (>= 0.9.4), RcppArmadillo (>= 0.2.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
